be shown is the combination

00:05:10.766 --> 00:05:14.066 A:middle
of your app's relevance to the
search query and the amount

00:05:14.066 --> 00:05:15.226 A:middle
of your bid comparative

00:05:15.226 --> 00:05:16.996 A:middle
to others bidding
on that same query.

00:05:18.006 --> 00:05:19.406 A:middle
And as I said earlier, apps

00:05:19.546 --> 00:05:22.686 A:middle
that aren't relevant won't
be entered into the auction.

